                           <type>QVariant</type>
                           <return_description>Header value if this is a row else an empty variant.</return_description>
                           <operation>If the given orientation is not vertical or the role is not the display role then return an empty variant.</operation>
                           <operation>Get a pointer _edit_ of this object's parent list edit widget. If casting this object's parent as a list edit widget fails then throw an exception.</operation>
                           <operation>Return a string title that is the list item title for _edit_ appended with the row's index plus one.</operation>
                        </data>
