         <class type="4">
            <data version="0">
               <name>Variable</name>
               <description>This is the variable block. This represents any global, class member, or function argument variable. This is also used as the base class for template arguments. This supports the constant expression, static, and mutable properties. The properties are checked to see if those properties make sense and an exception is thrown if one is set that is not valid. This also supports having an initial value.</description>
               <qtobject/>
            </data>
